			<DIV>I agree with the population idea trynd but then we come back to square 1. People do not like change, even in the pvp environment. If you start one way then change by opening up a new expansion people may leave and say well sony just messed up. I think if they start with kunark and velius open it will keep people happy. Lvl 60 cap with no AA's would work out just fine.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>The basic idea for a PvP server is to lvl up get some gear and spend the rest of the time PvPing over mobs, zones etc. Maybe even open up a few AA abilities but leave out the one shot kills.</DIV>	
